        "AGENTS.md says roadmap items should be chunky and dependency-aware, and queue-shaping work should prefer follow-up tasks over tiny fragmented tickets.",
        "`.ralph/README.md` defines `.ralph/queue.jsonc` as the source of truth for active work.",
        "`docs/queue-and-tasks.md:114-156` defines the canonical audit/scan follow-up flow via `.ralph/cache/followups/<TASK_ID>.json` plus `ralph task followups apply`, so remediation tasks should be proposed through that path rather than hand-edited into the queue.",
        "`docs/index.md:20`, `docs/guides/project-operating-constitution.md:79-94`, and `docs/roadmap.md:8-18` currently disagree with lived work: the roadmap is still a 2026-04-01 single-item file-splitting list while the active queue is already driving a broader audit/remediation effort.",
        "`docs/guides/project-operating-constitution.md:62-63` and `:121` require important decisions to be recorded, but `docs/decisions.md` still contains only the constitution-adoption entry while README documents project-level policy such as safe-default init, app noninteractive runs, and `make agent-ci` as the everyday gate.",
        "`crates/ralph/src/commands/run/parallel/args.rs:19-20`, `:26-130`, and `:266-340` show parallel worker argv strings duplicated by hand with tests that snapshot literals rather than parser round-tripping against the real CLI.",
        "`crates/ralph/src/contracts/machine.rs:34-45` centralizes many machine document versions in one file, but coverage in `crates/ralph/tests/machine_contract_test.rs` and adjacent tests is uneven across graph/dashboard/decompose/CLI-spec/run-summary surfaces.",
        "`crates/ralph/src/commands/task/mod.rs:48-273` and `crates/ralph/src/commands/daemon/mod.rs:71-213` still behave like mixed-responsibility command hubs instead of thin facades, increasing cross-cutting edit risk.",
        "`apps/RalphMac/RalphCore/MachineContract.swift:26-45`, `apps/RalphMac/RalphCore/Workspace+CLISpec.swift:156-182`, and `apps/RalphMac/RalphCore/RalphCLIArgumentBuilder.swift:31-107` duplicate CLI/app contract and argv rules across multiple app surfaces.",
