        "apps/RalphMac/RalphCore/WorkspaceRunnerController+MachineOutput.swift",
        "apps/RalphMac/RalphCoreTests/WorkspaceRunStateResumeBlockingTests.swift",
        "docs/machine-contract.md"
      ],
      "evidence": [
        "`crates/ralph/src/cli/machine/run.rs` emits a hardcoded loop terminal summary with `outcome: \"completed\"` and `blocking: None` after `run_loop(...)` succeeds.",
        "`crates/ralph/src/commands/run/run_loop/orchestration.rs` returns `Ok(())` for no initial todo tasks, no runnable candidates, and blocked tasks when not waiting.",
        "`apps/RalphMac/RalphCore/WorkspaceRunnerController+MachineOutput.swift` clears live blocking when a terminal run summary has no blocking payload.",
        "Live probe on an empty initialized repo emitted `run_started`, `resume_decision`, then `{\"version\":2,\"task_id\":null,\"exit_code\":0,\"outcome\":\"completed\"}` while stderr said `No todo tasks found.`"
